    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction: entry in Addenda listing on July 3 Media Business page about naming of Martin Shaw as creative director at an advertising agency misstated name of agency, which is Posner Advertising, not Posner Communications</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An entry in the Addenda listing on the Media Business page on Monday about the naming of Martin Shaw as creative director at an advertising agency misstated the name of the agency. It is Posner Advertising, not Posner Communications.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>An entry in the Addenda listing on the Media Business page on Monday about the naming of Martin Shaw as creative director at an advertising agency misstated the name of the agency. It is Posner Advertising, not Posner Communications.</p>
      </block>
    </body.content>
